\id ISA Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h ISAIAH
\toc1 ISAIAH
\toc2 Isaiah
\toc3 Isa
\mt1 ISAIAH
\mt2 (The Book of the Prophet Isaiah)
\is1 Isaiah Cabu Kawng
\im Isaiah he Olkhueh Rhuem dongah tah a sen koek la om. Hlohlailung a dung ngai neh ngaiuepnah ol muep a tael. Isaiah he tuithim kah Judah ram kho a sak tih 742-698 \sc b.c\sc* tluk vaengah Pathen loh a voeknah te a thui. Isaiah dongkah a ngen tah 538 \sc b.c\sc* vangsawn lamkah a mael phoeiah a tael. Te dongah Isaiah he hlang panit pathum kah a tael te rhen a cong coini tila poeknah om. Judah khohmu rhoek loh Pathen kah tiktamnah neh sitlohnah, thinphoei lungvatnah te hlohlailung la muep a tael. Isaiah he hlop thum la a boel. A pacuek dongah tah pilnam loh Boeipa kah tungaepnah te uepnah pawt tih Moses kah olkhueng a hnawt dongah Pathen kah ollcaeknah a pai ham, thunkha loh a muk vetih amih a tuuk ham khaw a rhalrhing sak. can be divided into three parts. A pabae dongah tah vangsawn kah pilnam taengah ngaiuepnah te omngaih koehnah hlohlailung la a thui. Pathen loh pilnam te a ram la a mael puei vetih Jerusalem bawkim koep a sak uh ham khaw a thui pah. A hnukhueng kah dongah tah pilnam koep a thohnah, Boeipa kah khohnin thai a saenah kawng te a thui.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Isaiah a Pacuek: Vangsawn Hlankah \ior 1. 1—39. 8\ior*
\io1 Isaiah a Pabae: Vangsawn pilnam ham olthangthen \ior 40. 1—55. 13\ior*
\io1 Isaiah a Pathum: Pilnam aka mael ham olthangthen \ior 56. 1—66. 24\ior*
\c 1
\p 
